629. BMJ. 2022 Oct 31;379:e071281. doi: 10.1136/bmj-2022-071281.

Clinical and cost effectiveness of single stage compared with two stage revision 
for hip prosthetic joint infection (INFORM): pragmatic, parallel group, open 
label, randomised controlled trial.

Blom AW(1)(2), Lenguerrand E(3), Strange S(3), Noble SM(4), Beswick AD(3), 
Burston A(3), Garfield K(4)(5), Gooberman-Hill R(3)(2), Harris SRS(4)(5), 
