Analysis of prognostic factors in patients with brain metastases affecting 
survival.

Gupta S(1), Singh S(2), Chophy A(2), Nair S(2), Ahuja R(2), Kusum K(3), Joseph 
D(2), Arora R(4), Gupta A(5), Gupta M(2).
